Career Center






	Carrizo provides a great work environment and benefit package.

	Carrizo has steadily grown for 20+ years and now employs more than 225 employees in four states. We offer an excellent work environment at a fast growing independent exploration and production company. At Carrizo, we understand that our human capital is critical to our success; thus, we recruit self-motivated, goal-oriented people who wish to support our corporate mission, while working hard towards their own success and that of the organization.

	Carrizo offers a highly competitive compensation package that fairly rewards each employee’s contributions and success, including aggressive short and long-term incentive programs. We offer comprehensive medical, dental and vision benefit programs, with a significant portion of insurance premiums covered for our employees and their families. In addition, we offer many other employer-provided and voluntary benefit programs.

	Carrizo is firm in its efforts to provide a work environment free from discrimination and harassment. We recruit, retain, train and promote employees without bias to race, gender, color, religion, pregnancy, sexual orientation, national origin, age, physical or mental disability, genetic information, citizenship status, veteran status, or any other category protected by law.


Fraudulent Recruiting Scam Alert
	 
It has come to our attention that falsified employment offer letters containing information regarding Carrizo Oil & Gas, Inc., the company logo, and names of management are being sent via email to individuals for fictitious job vacancies.  
	 
These emails and offer letters appear to be legitimate.  However, the letter typically includes a requirement to provide sensitive, personal information such as a passport number.  Additionally, we are aware that some letters request advanced fees from the individual for expenses such as work permits, preliminary relocation costs, etc.
	 
Please be aware that it is Carrizo’s recruiting practice to contact the applicant directly, conduct a formal application process, and personal interview with at least one member of management in a Company office location.  This process will occur prior to the extension of any offer of employment.  Carrizo does not request any advanced fees or upfront payments at any point in the recruiting process.  
	 
Please ignore any such emails or offers of employment from these fraudulent and illegal sources that have no affiliation with Carrizo Oil and Gas.  

	Mail Resume To:

	Carrizo Oil & Gas, Inc.

	ATTN: Human Resources
	500 Dallas St., Suite 2300
	Houston, TX 77002
 




