Who We Are
Carrizo Oil & Gas, Inc. is a Houston-based energy company actively engaged in the exploration, development, and production of oil and gas from resource plays located in the United States. Our current operations are principally focused in proven, producing oil and gas shale plays.

Read More






Where We Operate

	Our current operations are principally focused in the Eagle Ford Shale in South Texas, the Delaware Basin in West Texas, the Utica Shale in Ohio, the Niobrara Formation in Colorado, and the Marcellus Shale in Pennsylvania.

View Our Operations









Landowner Relations
We view our mineral owners and landowners as partners and seek to provide them with highest level of customer service. Our Landowner Relations team is to here to answer questions and concerns from our existing landowners, as well as prospective landowners interested in leasing with Carrizo.
Learn More

Careers with Carrizo
Carrizo offers a highly competitive compensation and benefits package, including bonus earnings potential and restricted stock incentives. Our benefit plan is designed to meet the diverse needs of our employees and their families.
Learn More















 



